┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  USER ENTERS: "Hi" or opens widget                      │
└────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────┘
                     ↓
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  WELCOME INTENT                                         │
│  Bot: "Hi! I'm NutriWell Coach. What would you like to  │
│        work on today?"                                  │
│  Shows Chips: [Set Goals] [Get Meal Plan] [Reminders]   │
└────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────┘
                     ↓
         ┌───────────┴────────────┐
         │                        │
    User clicks            User types
    "Set My Goals"         "Meal plan please"
         │                        │
         ↓                        ↓
┌─────────────────┐      ┌─────────────────────┐
│ SET FITNESS GOAL│      │ REQUEST MEAL PLAN   │
│ Intent          │      │ Intent (no context) │
└────────┬────────┘      └──────────┬──────────┘
         │                         │
         ↓                         ↓
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Bot asks: "What fitness goal? (weight loss/  │
│           muscle gain/maintenance/endurance)"│
└─────────────────┬────────────────────────────┘
                  ↓
    User responds: "lose weight"
                  ↓
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ SET DIETARY RESTRICTION Intent                 │
│ Input Context: awaiting_dietary_restrictions   │
│ Bot: "Any dietary restrictions? (vegan/veg/   │
│      gluten-free/dairy-free/keto)"           │
└─────────────────┬────────────────────────────┘
                  ↓
    User says: "vegan"
                  ↓
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ SET BUDGET PREFERENCE Intent                   │
│ Input Context: awaiting_budget                 │
│ Bot: "What's your budget? (low/medium/high)" │
└─────────────────┬────────────────────────────┘
                  ↓
    User says: "low"
                  ↓
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ SET TIME AVAILABILITY Intent                   │
│ Input Context: awaiting_time                   │
│ Bot: "How much prep time? (very quick/quick/  │
│      moderate/long)"                           │
└─────────────────┬────────────────────────────┘
                  ↓
    User says: "quick"
                  ↓
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ REQUEST MEAL PLAN Intent                       │
│ Input Context: awaiting_meal_plan              │
│ Bot: "Here's your plan! [Shows meals] Want    │
│      reminders?"                               │
│ Shows Chips: [Set Water Reminder] [Set       │
│              Exercise Reminder] [Main Menu]  │
└─────────────────┬────────────────────────────┘
                  ↓
         ┌────────┴────────┐
         │                 │
    User clicks      User clicks
    "Set Water       "Set Exercise
    Reminder"        Reminder"
         │                 │
         ↓                 ↓
┌─────────────────┐ ┌──────────────────┐
│ SET HYDRATION   │ │ SET EXERCISE     │
│ REMINDER Intent │ │ REMINDER Intent  │
└─────────────────┘ └──────────────────┘
         │                 │
         └────────┬────────┘
                  ↓
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Bot: "Reminder set! What would you like to   │
│      do next?"                                 │
│ Shows Chips: [Track Progress] [Get Motivation│
│              ] [View Meal Plan]              │
└─────────────────┬────────────────────────────┘
                  ↓
         ┌────────┴────────────────┐
         │                         │
    User says           User says
    "Track my weight"   "I need motivation"
         │                         │
         ↓                         ↓
┌─────────────────┐      ┌──────────────────┐
│ TRACK PROGRESS  │      │ REQUEST MOTIVATION│
│ Intent          │      │ Intent           │
└─────────────────┘      └──────────────────┘
         │                         │
         ↓                         ↓
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ END OF CONVERSATION / FALLBACK TO MAIN MENU  │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────┘

KEY:
┌───┐ = Intent (Bot Function)
│   │ = User Input
─── = Flow
┴─┬─┴ = Decision/Branch
